&lt;p&gt;So, you&amp;rsquo;ve made the decision to move to Japan with your spouse - congratulations! Now, here comes the bureaucracy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My wife is a Japanese national so naturally we applied for my Spouse Visa. This is one of several categories of visas that the country of Japan can issue. The full name of this visa is the &lt;em&gt;Spouse or Child of Japanese National&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
